# Nomlog app (monorepo package)

- Use **pnpm**, not Yarn. Install and lockfile live at the **repo root**; see root `README.md` and `.cursor/rules/package-manager.mdc`.
- Typical commands from repo root: `pnpm --filter nomlog-app run start`, `pnpm --filter nomlog-app run ios`, etc.
- Do not change the pinned `packageManager` version in `package.json` unless the user asks for a toolchain upgrade.

# Agent rules

- Always state agent model and version used in summary of changes
